    <h5 class="card-title">Statue of unity</h5>
    <p class="card-text">The Statue of Unity is the world's tallest statue,
	 with a height of 182 metres (597 feet),[3] located near Kevadia in the state of Gujarat, India.
	  It depicts Indian statesman and independence activist Vallabhbhai Patel (1875–1950), 
	who was the first deputy prime minister and home minister of independent India </p>
